headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Canis Kamacho
content: There’s only one thing you look for in a 4x4: simplicity. The simplicity of big wheels, an indestructible chassis, a cargo bed full of beer, and a few hundred angry horses under the hood. The Canis Kamacho has come to deliver all that, and pretty much nothing else – because anything more would just weigh you down.
